payload
-------
{"operationName":"GetPreferences","variables":{"objectType":"Grid","objectName":"Admin","pageName":"SettingsAdmin"},"query":"query GetPreferences($objectType: String!, $objectName: String!, $pageName: String!) {\n  preferences(\n    objectType: $objectType\n    objectName: $objectName\n    pageName: $pageName\n  ) {\n    data {\n      pageName\n      objectType\n      objectName\n      preferenceDetail\n      __typename\n    }\n    isSuccess\n    message\n    errorCode\n    __typename\n  }\n}"}

--------

        "preferences": {
            "data": {
                "pageName": "SettingsAdmin",
                "objectType": "Grid",
                "objectName": "Admin",

-------
